title: Too slippery. Don't buy this

title: 'Better than expected'
body: I thought it was going to be like regular quality playing cards found in local stores but to my surprise the quality of the cards are incredible, i dont know what it's made out of but I can tell you that it is not made of regular thin cardboard that easily wears out overtime. It would make the product better if the prints on the cards are a bit more saturated.
